rComments: One of the best French professors I've ever had. If I knew she was teaching another course, I would honestly enrol in a heartbeat if I could. She is extremely caring about her students and quite theatrical - she's the perfect balance of entertaining and hard-working, fun and "serious".

Professor Bouchard is so sweet and caring! I would absolutely love her to teach all of my classes. She's funny and personable and wants you to succeed. If you participate and do your work, you'll do well.  Her slides have lots of information on it, which she posts, so you can absolutely pay attention in lecture rather than have to take notes.
